OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777546976
OL,3,CPolice raid religious group over
OL,4,C'forced marriage and modern slavery'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FA religious group in Cheshire has been
OL,8,Fraided by police investigating
OL,9,Fallegations of sexual abuse, forced
OL,10,Fmarriage and people trafficking.
OL,12,FSix people were arrested when officers
OL,13,Fstormed three locations linked to the
OL,14,FCrewe-based Ahmadi Religion of Peace
OL,15,Fand Light, including the headquarters
OL,16,Fon Victoria Avenue.
OL,18,FCheshire Police said the alleged
OL,19,Foffences involved one victim, a woman,
OL,20,Fwho was a member of the group at the
OL,21,Ftime the offences occurred.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
