PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777546976
OL,3,CPolice raid religious group over
OL,4,C'forced marriage and modern slavery'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FChief Superintendent Gareth Wrigley
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our policing activity and
OL,9,Fongoing, complex investigation relates
OL,10,Fto allegations of serious sexual
OL,11,Foffences, forced marriage and modern
OL,12,Fslavery.
OL,14,F"I must stress at this point, we are
OL,15,Finvestigating those offences, and we
OL,16,Fare not investigating the religious
OL,17,Fgroup."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777546976
OL,3,CPolice raid religious group over
OL,4,C'forced marriage and modern slavery'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FMore than 500 officers from Cheshire
OL,8,FPolice and neighbouring forces were
OL,9,Finvolved in the operation and the six
OL,10,Farrested are four males and two
OL,11,Ffemales of American, Mexican, Italian,
OL,12,FSpanish and British nationalities.
OL,14,FThey remain in custody as searches of
OL,15,Fthe premises continue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
