OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777546976
OL,3,CPolice raid religious group over
OL,4,C'forced marriage and modern slavery'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FChief Superintendent Wrigley, added:
OL,8,F"Today's operation is the outcome of a
OL,9,Fdetailed and robust investigation into
OL,10,Freports of serious sexual offences,
OL,11,Fforced marriage and modern slavery
OL,12,Finvolving members of a religious group
OL,13,Fcalled Ahmadi Religion of Peace and
OL,14,FLight in Crewe.
OL,16,F"While those arrested are members of
OL,17,Fthe group, I want to make clear that
OL,18,Fthis is not an investigation into the
OL,19,Freligion, this is an investigation
OL,20,Finto the serious allegations which
OL,21,Fhave been reported to us.
OL,26,@pD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
