PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777546976
OL,3,CPolice raid religious group over
OL,4,C'forced marriage and modern slavery'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"We treat all reports of sexual
OL,8,Fassault seriously and are committed to
OL,9,Fdoing all we can to achieve justice.
OL,11,F"Following the arrests we are working
OL,12,Fclosely with our partners to provide
OL,13,Fthe appropriate advice and
OL,14,Fsafeguarding to other members of the
OL,15,Fgroup.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
